{"tid":1783063,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【殺人放火金腰帶】【唉，移民啦】警隊多名高層據報獲晉升","createTime":"2019-12-14T13:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T13:23:50.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91e6b37198fd38cb5be56408f4f8d985e1f16537","tid":1783063,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%8D%B2%E6%99%89%E5%8D%87-%E9%99%B6%E8%BC%9D-%E8%8E%8A%E5%AE%9A%E8%B3%A2%E5%B0%87%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2599%2589%25E5%258D%2587-%25E9%2599%25B6%25E8%25BC%259D-%25E8%258E%258A%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=37194970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2599%2589%25E5%258D%2587-%25E9%2599%25B6%25E8%25BC%259D-%25E8%258E%258A%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%2F&h=1d78ca5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E7%8D%B2%E6%99%89%E5%8D%87-%E9%99%B6%E8%BC%9D-%E8%8E%8A%E5%AE%9A%E8%B3%A2%E5%B0%87%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7/</a><br />\n<br />\n警隊多名高層據報獲晉升 陶輝、莊定賢將任助理處長<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒引述消息指，警隊下週將會公布新一輪升職名單，當中助理處長蔡展鵬和林曉彤都獲晉升為高級助理處長，當中蔡展鵬被指為「隔代一哥」人選之一。至於在反送中運動當中，多次指揮行動的機動部隊校長莊定賢（David Jordan）、以及署理新界南總區指揮官陶輝（Rupert Dover），都會由總警司晉升至助理處長。<br />\n<br />\n《成報》和《東方日報》昨日和今日都報道了警隊中高層人員的升職消息。現時主管保安部的蔡展鵬，專責有關保安事務的情報行動、調查、分析與聯絡工作。他在 1995 年加入警隊，由督察開始做起。他在 2017 年 6 月升為總警司，今年 1 月升為助理處長。<br />\n<br />\n至於另一名有望升為高級助理處長的林曉彤，在 1989 年 7 月加入警隊，她曾經在 2006 至 2007 年被借調到保安局擔任助理秘書長。她在 2017 年 9 月出任助理警務處長（支援），在去年中，她曾經以助理社團事務主任身份撰寫報告給保安局，建議引用《社團條例》條文，禁止香港民族黨運作。<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動持續多月，當中在 6.12 衝突當中，警方事隔 4 年多再次在金鐘發射多枚催淚彈，隸屬新界南總區的總警司陶輝有份在現場指揮，而機動部隊校長莊定賢就負責帶領速龍小隊行動。上述兩位外籍警官都曾經處理 2014 年的佔領運動，他們事後都雙雙在 2016 年獲頒「行政長官公共服務獎狀」。報道指，兩人都會獲晉升為助理處長。<br />\n<br />\n除了莊定賢和陶輝之外，早前有份處理工大學示威，包括籌備安全小組的署理助理處長（行動）周一鳴，有份主管應變大隊的港島總區總警司呂錦豪、保安部總警司江學禮據報都會獲升為助理處長。"},{"pid":"a2018d8c6f9cf8fa2bea98aad33d5d261a1be7ab","tid":1783063,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:14:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zrNpRn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrNpRn5.jpg&h=7453738e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Hhk89N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Hhk89N.jpg&h=e421777a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPC5APO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPC5APO.jpg&h=08184019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"404ff404e9a5ce84e39b011f0dbbebfeb029b5b3","tid":1783063,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=978092f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nGroup List&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/186\" data-sr-url=